[SHORT DESC]
Ignores accuracy modifiers.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Faint Attack ignores all accuracy and evasion modifiers.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/magnet_bomb">Magnet Bomb</a> is a Steel-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/shadow_punch">Shadow Punch</a> is a Ghost-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/faint_attack">Aerial Ace</a> is a Flying-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/swift">Swift</a> is a Normal-type equivalent, but is special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/magical_leaf/">Magical Leaf</a> is a Grass-type equivalent, but is special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/shock_wave">Shock Wave</a> is an Electric-type equivalent, but is special.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/bite">Bite</a> is almost identical, but can miss if accuracy modifiers are present and has a chance to flinch.</p>